article.headline: Derkack's 19 lead Merrimack over Le Moyne 66-62
article.description: — Jordan Derkack scored 19 points as Merrimack beat Le Moyne 66-62 on Saturday.
article.linkText: Derkack's 19 lead Merrimack over Le Moyne 66-62
article.story: SYRACUSE, N.Y. -- — Jordan Derkack scored 19 points as Merrimack beat Le Moyne 66-62 on Saturday. Derkack added seven rebounds for the Warriors (9-8, 3-0 Northeast Conference). Adam Clark scored 10 points and added five assists. Bryan Etumnu finished 4 of 6 from the field to finish with nine points. The Dolphins (6-10, 1-1) were led by Kaiyem Cleary, who posted 16 points. Le Moyne also got 10 points from Nate Fouts. In addition, AJ Dancier finished with seven points and six rebounds. NEXT UP Both teams next play Monday. Merrimack visits Cent. Conn. St. and Le Moyne plays Sacred Heart at home. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
